location.fullValue: Roffee Plan, Guadalupe Heights : Barrington Collection

data.description: This gorgeous three bedroom two bath home is only three years old and has great neighborhood amenities that include a pool, club house, walking trails and playground. Island kitchen w/granite counters, stainless appliances and nice pantry. Carpet in the bedrooms and wood look flooring everywhere else. Master suite has a walk in closet and walk in shower. Ceiling fans throughout. Two car garage. Covered patio and privacy fenced backyard for year round outdoor entertaining and new roof.
